{"tid":1959870,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國年輕靚仔護士染疫死亡","createTime":"2020-04-05T17:34:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-06T01:30:17.000Z","uid":42188,"like":2,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"e0797aaa31b11b30754985447cb1ba4ae15c3f68","tid":1959870,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T17:34:48.000Z","msg":"英國一名年輕男護士在工作期間感到不適，但由於醫院人手不足而不獲准回家，最後下班回家後死亡，屬英國第3名患病死亡的護士。據了解，他在工作期間沒有足夠合適的防護裝備。<br />\n<br />\n23歲的阿拉戈斯（John Alagos）在沃特福德綜合醫院（Watford General Hospital）工作，有份照顧武漢肺炎患者，他周五輪班12小時下班回家，表示整晚都感到頭痛和發燒，最後在家中離世。阿拉戈斯相信是英國最年輕染疫死亡的醫護人員。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0jDXJFX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0jDXJFX.png&h=e492f173&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好想含<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c33788ea2877112415249a3eb5c8d9a9993dd3a","tid":1959870,"uid":154054,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T17:39:12.000Z","msg":"23歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />RIP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33010cb79973233935f988ac228705baff3f8dc8","tid":1959870,"uid":215755,"like":1,"dislike":56,"score":-55,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T17:43:02.000Z","msg":"男人做護士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b062fabc45558aa89eba1508c268a687f724313","tid":1959870,"uid":51698,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"33010cb79973233935f988ac228705baff3f8dc8","tid":1959870,"uid":215755,"like":1,"dislike":56,"score":-55,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T17:43:02.000Z","msg":"男人做護士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T17:46:47.000Z","msg":"有咩問題？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢出現病徵一晚就死咗會唔會本身有隱疾？"},{"pid":"09c475a6fcf4a5f